  <reg:title>Mineral Tax Return Form Regulation</reg:title>
  <reg:amsincluded>[includes amendments up to B.C. Reg. 188/2015, December 1, 2015]</reg:amsincluded>
  <reg:regpitid>86_98_pit</reg:regpitid>
  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section id="d2e31" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Form of returns</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e39">
        <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>A return delivered by an operator of a mine to the commissioner under section 12 (1) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96291_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Mineral Tax Act</in:doc></bcl:link> must be in the form set out in Schedule A.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e51">
        <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>A return delivered by an operator of a placer gold mine to the commissioner under section 12 (1.1) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96291_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Mineral Tax Act</in:doc></bcl:link> must be in the form set out in Schedule C.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e63">
        <bcl:num>3</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>A return delivered by a quarry operator to the commissioner under section 12 (1.2) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96291_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Mineral Tax Act</in:doc></bcl:link> must be in the form set out in Schedule D.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e76">
        <bcl:num>4</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>A return delivered for an operator's exploration account under section 12 (7) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96291_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Mineral Tax Act</in:doc></bcl:link> must be in the form set out in Schedule E.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:hnote>[am. B.C. Regs. 272/99, s. 1; 431/2000, s. 1; 287/2002, ss. (a) and (b).]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
